Exercise: IA rectangle is divided in half by an imaginary line from the upper-right corner to the lower-left corner. Of the divided rectangle, the left triangle is totally white and the right rectangle is totally black. There’s no grey in this picture. Don’t draw the imaginary line. 

Answer: (image-show (psaifr-greyscale-image (lambda (x y) (sign (+ x y))) 100 100 10))